Title: TracPipe coupling 50mm
Description: Manufactured in brass, this TracPipe 50mm coupling with AutoFlare connection is part of the comprehensive TracPipe range. Made up of pliable corrugated stainless steel gas pipes, TracPipe is an un-annealed alternative to rigid copper or steel. Highly resistant to damage and crushing, TracPipe is ideal  for site work and for use in industrial or commercial applications, offering suitability for external or internal use. It can also be buried in the ground or in screed with no need for corrosion or mechanical protection. Four times stronger than equivalent products, TracPipe features a polyethylene cover incorporating flame spread and smoke density inhibitors for high levels of compliance.
